wdi2-TX.VAL.MRCH.AL.ZS.def: Merchandise exports to economies in the Arab World are the sum of merchandise exports by the reporting economy to economies in the Arab World. Data are expressed as a percentage of total merchandise exports by the economy. Data are computed only if at least half of the economies in the partner country group had non-missing data.
wdi2-TX.VAL.MRCH.AL.ZS.name: Merchandise exports to economies in the Arab World
wdi2-TX.VAL.MRCH.AL.ZS.source: World Bank staff estimates based data from International Monetary Fund's Direction of Trade database.
